Steps to install CocoaPods

1) sudo gem install cocoapods
2) pod setup --verbose
3) Locate to project and create pod file using command (pod init)
4) To Update - sudo gem install cocoapods --pre
5) Open POD and give the version for download (pod 'socket.IO', '~> 0.5.2')
6) Navigate to your project and run the command (pod install)
